name: I'll Take Them Myself
Lore: '''Several fighters have broken off from the main group. Come with me.'' Darth Vader targets his TIE fighter''s fire-linked blaster cannons at the Rebel pilots in the trench.',
Text: 'Deploy on table.  Once per game, may take a [Setup] card into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.  May place this card in Used Pile to take an Immediate Effect into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.  May place this Effect in Lost Pile to cancel a Force drain. (Immune to Alter.)',
